[SN]TITLE[SN]
Road reopens after lorry overturns on A4042 in Newport

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The northbound carriageway of the A4042 has reopened following an earlier incident where a lorry overturned.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The driver of the lorry was taken to hospital after his vehicle tipped over on the slip road on to the Grove Park roundabout in Newport.
South Wales Fire and Rescue Service sent two crews following the incident just before 11:15 BST on Tuesday.
The road was reopened at 16:00 BST, however the residual delays remain.
